{"id":285542,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/global-voices-在北京抽免费的烟/","date":"2013-03-23T01:45:09Z","modified":"2013-03-23T01:45:09Z","title":"Global Voices | 在北京抽免费的烟","content":"<p><p>身为前Google中国区总裁和一位具影响力的李开复，在他拥有三千两百万粉丝的微博上<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/login.php?url=http%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F1197161814%2Fznd5C1WAw%3Futm_\">发表</a>了一则虚构的北京人与上海人的对话：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>北京人：“我们北京人最幸福，打开窗子就有免费的烟。”上海人：“那算什么，我们打开自来水就是排骨汤！”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>这个极具讽刺意味的对话暗指了北京所发生的严重空气污染和南京黄埔江上游水源地发现<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/03/12/thousands-of-dead-pigs-found-floating-in-shanghai-river/\">死猪的事件</a>。这则对话自2013年三月13日发表后被转发了超过61,790次。</p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/abby/\" title=\"文章导读 Abby\">Abby</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/neon/\" title=\"文章导读 neon\">neon</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/03/13/china-beijings-free-cigarettes-and-shanghais-pork-soup/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/03/23/12331/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%8A%BD%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E7%9A%84%E7%83%9F&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F03%2F23%2F12331%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F03%2F23%2F12331%2F&#038;desc=%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%8A%BD%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E7%9A%84%E7%83%9F\" title=\"MyShare